{"segment":13,"line_start":540,"line_end":586,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"你怎么知道我认得他？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":28,"line_start":540,"line_end":540},{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"你当然知道，无论谁都应该看得出，我是去找他的。","tone":"无奈","chapter":28,"line_start":542,"line_end":544},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"找他干什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":546,"line_end":546},{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"也不干什么，只不过想把他的脑袋切下来，一脚踢到阴沟里去。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":28,"line_start":548,"line_end":550},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"他是你的仇人？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":552,"line_end":552},{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"本来不是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":554,"line_end":554},{"speaker":"char_gan_che_xiao_huo_zi","speaker_name":"赶车小伙子","listener":null,"text":"本来他是我的朋友。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":556,"line_end":556},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"朋友？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":558,"line_end":558},{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"朋友有时比仇人还可怕，更可怕，尤其是像他这样的朋友。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":28,"line_start":560,"line_end":562},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"你上过他的当？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":564,"line_end":564},{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"我把全副家当都交付了他，把我最喜欢的女人也交给了他，但他却溜了，带着我的全副家当和我的女人溜了。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":28,"line_start":566,"line_end":568},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"看来他倒不像是个这么样的人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":570,"line_end":570},{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"就因为他不像，所以我才会信任他。","tone":"沉声","chapter":28,"line_start":572,"line_end":572},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"朋友有时的确比仇人还可怕。","tone":"恐惧","chapter":28,"line_start":574,"line_end":574},{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"你从来都没有朋友？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":576,"line_end":576},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"没有。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":578,"line_end":578},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"茶客","listener":null,"text":"你本来不必陪我走的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":582,"line_end":582},{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"的确不必，本来我们可以一起坐在车上。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":584,"line_end":584}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_xue_da_han","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":28,"line_start":548,"line_end":568,"text":"薛大汉说路小佳原是朋友，却带走他的全副家当和女人，因此要取其头。"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"add","target":"char_lu_xiao_jia","type":"宿敌","intensity":88,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"由朋友变仇人，因家当和女人被带走而追杀"}]},{"id":"char_lu_xiao_jia","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":28,"line_start":556,"line_end":568,"text":"薛大汉称路小佳曾是朋友，后带走他的家当和女人。"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"add","target":"char_xue_da_han","type":"对手","intensity":80,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"被薛大汉视为背信朋友和追杀对象"}]}]}
{"segment":14,"line_start":588,"line_end":640,"dialogues":[{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"茶客","listener":null,"text":"喝口酒？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":588,"line_end":588},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"不喝。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":590,"line_end":590},{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"你从来都不喝酒？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":592,"line_end":592},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"从来不喝。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":594,"line_end":594},{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"赌钱呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":596,"line_end":596},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"从来不赌。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":598,"line_end":598},{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"你喜欢干什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":600,"line_end":600},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"什么都不喜欢。","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":602,"line_end":602},{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"一个人若是什么都不喜欢，活着还有乐趣？","tone":"无奈","chapter":28,"line_start":604,"line_end":604},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"我本不是为了有趣而活着的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":606,"line_end":606},{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"你活着是为了什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":608,"line_end":608},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"为了复仇。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":610,"line_end":610},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"茶客","listener":null,"text":"看来做你的仇人，的确不是件愉快的事。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":28,"line_start":612,"line_end":614},{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"你是不是也认得路小佳？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":618,"line_end":618},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"我只见过他。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":620,"line_end":620},{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"怎么会见到的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":622,"line_end":622},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"他想来杀我。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":624,"line_end":624},{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"后来呢？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":28,"line_start":626,"line_end":626},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"后来他就走了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":628,"line_end":628},{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"你就让他走？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":630,"line_end":630},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"我并不想杀他……我想杀的只有一个人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":632,"line_end":632},{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"你的仇人？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":634,"line_end":634},{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"你的仇人只有一个？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":638,"line_end":638},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"现在我只知道一个。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":640,"line_end":640}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[{"id":"item_xue_da_han_jiu_hu_lu","name":"薛大汉酒葫芦","type":"special","owner":"char_xue_da_han","one_line":"薛大汉随身携带的漆黑发亮酒葫芦。","description":"漆黑发亮的酒葫芦被薛大汉一路提着豪饮，也用来向傅红雪让酒，体现其粗豪嗜