{"segment":15,"line_start":642,"line_end":690,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"你的运气比我好。","tone":"无奈","chapter":28,"line_start":642,"line_end":642},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"其实你的运气比我好。","tone":"无奈","chapter":28,"line_start":644,"line_end":644},{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":646,"line_end":646},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"若有杀不尽的仇人可杀，倒也是人生一快，只可惜我……","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":648,"line_end":648},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"茶客","listener":null,"text":"只可惜我连那一个仇人都找不到。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":650,"line_end":652},{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"你那仇人是谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":654,"line_end":654},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"你不必知道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":656,"line_end":656},{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"但是我却说不定可以帮你找到他。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":658,"line_end":658},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"他姓马，马空群。","tone":"陈述","chapter":28,"line_start":660,"line_end":660},{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"万马堂的主人？","tone":"疑问","chapter":28,"line_start":662,"line_end":662},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","text":"你认得他！","tone":"惊讶","chapter":28,"line_start":664,"line_end":664},{"speaker":"char_xue_da_han","speaker_name":"薛大汉","listener":"char_fu_hong_xue","text":"这就难怪你要到白云庄去了！","tone":"喃喃","chapter":28,"line_start":666,"line_end":668},{"speaker":"char_fu_hong_xue","speaker_name":"傅红雪","listener":"char_cui_nong","t